The paper involves the combination of steganography, cryptography, and neural networks to hide data in images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves image processing and manipulation, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the use of AI techniques to improve the security of data hiding, which could also place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
